I believe you will do better than I think,  It is understandable that you may be a bit apprehensive because you do not know me, I am writing this mail to you with serious tears in my eyes and great sorrow in my heart, I decided to contact you due to the urgency of my situation. My Name is Mrs. Victoria Toyo, Am contacting you from my country USA. I want to tell you this because I don't have any other option than to tell you as I was touched to open up to you, I am married to Late Dr. Franklin Toyo who worked with USA Embassy in Ouagadougou the capital city of Burkina Faso for nine years before he died in the year 2005. We were married for eleven years without a child. He died after a brief illness that lasted for only five days. Since his death I decided not to remarry again, when my late husband was alive he deposited the sum of US$15 Million (Fifteen Million United States Dollars) with a bank in Ouagadougou,  Presently this money is still in the bank there. He made this money available for exportation of Gold from Burkina mining. Recently, My Doctor told me that I would not last for the period of seven months due to cancer problem. The one that disturbs me most is my stroke sickness. Having known my condition I decided to hand you over this mission to take care of the less-privileged, you will utilize this money the way I am going to instruct herein. I want you to take 30 Percent of the total money for your personal use While 70% of the money will go to charity work" helping people in the street.  Because I grew up as an Orphan and I don't have anybody as my family member, just to Endeavour that the house of God is maintained. Am doing this so that God will forgive my sins and accept my soul because this sickness has suffered me so much. As soon as I receive your reply I shall give you the contact of the bank in Burkina Faso and I will also instruct my lawyer to issue you an authority letter that will prove you the present beneficiary of the money in the bank that's if you assure me that you will act accordingly as I Stated herein. please, kindly reply me back through my private email address for more explanations. ( toyov@yahoo.com )  Remain blessed Yours Sister Mrs. Victoria Toyo.

Hello Dear, My name is Eric Goodwill, I am 53 years old, I came from Fort Bragg North Carolina United States of America. I am a U.S soldier currently serving with the army of the 3rd Infantry Division. My team is trained for dictating bombs and explosives and would apply caution and diffuse them. I am a widower; I lost my wife 5 years ago in car accident. May her gentle soul rest in peace. She left me with a girl who is 13 years old now, i came in contact with you, because I'm seeking for your friendship, understanding. Currently I'm in Syria with the 3rd Infantry Division. I am writing you about a business idea that will be of great benefit to us. During our raid, in one of the ISLE camp Aleppo, we discovered a huge amount of money, golds, desert diamonds, valued at $559,640,290.00 USD. We do not remit the entire funds to US government. We divided the fund in into two.  We sent one part to US Government, and the other part, we used UN security diplomat to move it to a secure location at the moment.  My wife died in auto crash, in 13 June 2012, when my wife died, I was currently serving in Afghanistan in the military with the army. My annual salary is not up to 30,000 USD annually all the funds go to my daughter's college fund. I engaged in this transaction because I wanted this money to help my life, and give my daughter a good life that she deserves. And establish a good business in good memory of my loving wife. Like buying house with sea view and establishing good business.  The senior officers involved in this deal want to share the funds and the diamonds. According to the sharing mode, I will be receiving cash and valued equivalent of$11,700,000.00 USD.  Right now I am looking for credible person who will be able to assist me to receive my share in cash, in your door step on a special arrangement with UN diplomatic envoy, I am in Syria currently, secondly I can’t use my US account to receive such huge amount of fund or involving anybody i know right now because of security reason, it will arise suspicions on me. I also wish to use my own share in any profitable business which you may introduce to me; I have no experience in business. I decided to seek your consent on this matter because of time constraint. After a lot of thoughts about this I decided to contact you because currently I am still serving in Syria which will make it impossible for me to carry out this transaction in America and also  considering the nature of my job, for security reasons, I will not be able to handle this transaction myself. I decided to contact you hoping that you will find this proposal interesting. The reason why I came to you with this proposal is because we are ready to share the money which is valued at $279,820,145 and according to the sharing agreement 16 army personal are involved, and the fund will be shared according to army ranks in my division. My share $11,700,000.00 USD If you are ready to work with me, I am ready to offer 30% of my total share while I will take 70% of the total fund. Before we proceed in this transaction, I will need your full contact details, is risky free, you have nothing to lose. I will give you any information you will need. I strongly want any government issuer ID card from you. Your Residential/office address I only require your honest cooperation to enable us see this transaction through. If I’m satisfied with your kind of person, So we can proceed.  Waiting to hear from you.  Eric Goodwill
